ome(\"repo:corvia\"), 0.8),\n            make_result(Some(\"design\"), Some(\"workspace\"), 0.7),\n        ];\n        let filtered = super::post_filter_metadata(results, None, Some(\"repo:corvia\"), None);\n        assert_eq!(filtered.len(), 2);\n    }\n\n    #[test]\n    fn test_post_filter_combined() {\n        let results = vec![",
